message.body: Hey. How's it going?
Sorry. I just got out of the shower. Its going ok.
You?
Good. I didn't train because she was sick. So I've had a lot of time to manually QC.
Also. Cassy just texted me about
Dorney. She made a mistake. It's the 14th. Not the 7th. Is that a problem?
Yes. I work.
And you're not allowed to move it?
Let her know you can't go?
I don't want to have to go in on Sunday instead and work six days straight. I really don't know.
Okay.
So I guess tell her no
If you change your mind we 'll have to get the ticket full price
This really sucks. How much?
I think $50 instead of $35. And then you can't go into the food area. But we can try to sneak you in or bring you out food.
Uh. I think not.
When does she need a decision?
When she told me last time she said by that Monday
That has already passed and I said yes. She hasn't bought tickets yet?
Ok. Do yup remember how late you got back last time?
Let me ask. I got back around 11 last time. I remember because I was surprised you said I could still come over. Those days.
Hah. Ok. I'm thinking of what I want to do: /

Because I'm just thinking of how to use my vacation days before October 15th. I think I have 3-4 days right now. I can take maybe one day a month this summer for a long weekend. I could take that following Friday off do I wouldn't have work six days straight. Ugh! Every other weekend sucks!
I know
Tell classy I'll go.
Are you sure
Yeah. I want to do fun things with you this summer.
Okay :)
I'm debating on taking a bath tonight. If I do, are you in?
With bells on.
Haha. With bells on? Haha.
Yeah. It's an expression.
